      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t要是「俄羅斯化」那中國可就進步了，應該是蘇聯化，或叫「赤化」，那跟赤化前差別挺大的。<br/>\n<br/>\n赤化前的親子關係<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMDdlNWU5MzU0MjRiMzU4YzkwYzM0LmpwZz93aWR0aD02NDAmaGVpZ2h0PTQ4NQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/07e5e935424b358c90c34.jpg?width=640&amp;height=485\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/07e5e935424b358c90c34.jpg?width=640&amp;height=485\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/07e5e935424b358c90c34.jpg?width=640&amp;height=485\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n赤化後的親子關係<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNWJjODk5MmZkZDQ2MjYzMjQ5OGRmLmpwZz93aWR0aD05MDAmaGVpZ2h0PTYwMA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5bc8992fdd462632498df.jpg?width=900&amp;height=600\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5bc8992fdd462632498df.jpg?width=900&amp;height=600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5bc8992fdd462632498df.jpg?width=900&amp;height=600\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n赤化前的頂流服飾<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNzI3ZmJiMzNlMTZkMGFiYzMwNWZiLmpwZz93aWR0aD04MDAmaGVpZ2h0PTgwMA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/727fbb33e16d0abc305fb.jpg?width=800&amp;height=800\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/727fbb33e16d0abc305fb.jpg?width=800&amp;height=800\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/727fbb33e16d0abc305fb.jpg?width=800&amp;height=800\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n赤化後的頂流服飾<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMjk3ZjA2NmE5NGRiOWZkOTIxOGE3LmpwZz93aWR0aD00OTgmaGVpZ2h0PTMzMw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/297f066a94db9fd9218a7.jpg?width=498&amp;height=333\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/297f066a94db9fd9218a7.jpg?width=498&amp;height=333\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/297f066a94db9fd9218a7.jpg?width=498&amp;height=333\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n赤化前的藝術創作<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYTBmZjhiMTQ0M2I3OGJmNWU5MGUzLmpwZz93aWR0aD02NDAmaGVpZ2h0PTEzMDI\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a0ff8b1443b78bf5e90e3.jpg?width=640&amp;height=1302\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a0ff8b1443b78bf5e90e3.jpg?width=640&amp;height=1302\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a0ff8b1443b78bf5e90e3.jpg?width=640&amp;height=1302\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n赤化後的藝術創作<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvOTM4YTM3MDliOTI5ZTY1YWMxNDYzLmpwZz93aWR0aD00MDAmaGVpZ2h0PTI3OA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/938a3709b929e65ac1463.jpg?width=400&amp;height=278\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/938a3709b929e65ac1463.jpg?width=400&amp;height=278\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/938a3709b929e65ac1463.jpg?width=400&amp;height=278\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n赤化前的豪情文學<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMzlhNThkNjBhZjdlMDVmNGJmYzZlLnBuZz93aWR0aD0xMDgwJmhlaWdodD00MzQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/39a58d60af7e05f4bfc6e.png?width=1080&amp;height=434\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/39a58d60af7e05f4bfc6e.png?width=1080&amp;height=434\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/39a58d60af7e05f4bfc6e.png?width=1080&amp;height=434\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n赤化後的豪情文學<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZDFjNjYxNGFkM2U0NmJkYTAxNTllLnBuZz93aWR0aD0xMDgwJmhlaWdodD0xMDkx\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/d1c6614ad3e46bda0159e.png?width=1080&amp;height=1091\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/d1c6614ad3e46bda0159e.png?width=1080&amp;height=1091\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/d1c6614ad3e46bda0159e.png?width=1080&amp;height=1091\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n赤化前的宗教禮拜形式<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMjVlYWJiYTkzMGFjZjkwMGZlMTk0LmpwZz93aWR0aD02MDAmaGVpZ2h0PTQyOQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/25eabba930acf900fe194.jpg?width=600&amp;height=429\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/25eabba930acf900fe194.jpg?width=600&amp;height=429\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/25eabba930acf900fe194.jpg?width=600&amp;height=429\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n赤化後的宗教禮拜形式<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMGE0OTdhMDI1NjhiMzQwZTRjYzIyLnBuZz93aWR0aD0xMDgwJmhlaWdodD04MDY\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/0a497a02568b340e4cc22.png?width=1080&amp;height=806\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/0a497a02568b340e4cc22.png?width=1080&amp;height=806\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/0a497a02568b340e4cc22.png?width=1080&amp;height=806\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n當然也有不變的....<br/>\n<br/>\n赤化前的政治制度<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZmE0ODE4NTg3ZDVkMDFiMDg3YzQyLmpwZz93aWR0aD0yMDAmaGVpZ2h0PTI4NQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/fa4818587d5d01b087c42.jpg?width=200&amp;height=285\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/fa4818587d5d01b087c42.jpg?width=200&amp;height=285\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/fa4818587d5d01b087c42.jpg?width=200&amp;height=285\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n赤化後的政治制度<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMjcwYTI0ZTA2NDVkNGM3MmMwNjZhLmpwZz93aWR0aD0yMDAmaGVpZ2h0PTI4NQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/270a24e0645d4c72c066a.jpg?width=200&amp;height=285\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/270a24e0645d4c72c066a.jpg?width=200&amp;height=285\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/270a24e0645d4c72c066a.jpg?width=200&amp;height=285\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n赤化前的群眾維權方式<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYmJiNTgwOGM0OWVmMDAyOWQxNmY0LnBuZz93aWR0aD0xMDgwJmhlaWdodD02NzE\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/bbb5808c49ef0029d16f4.png?width=1080&amp;height=671\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/bbb5808c49ef0029d16f4.png?width=1080&amp;height=671\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/bbb5808c49ef0029d16f4.png?width=1080&amp;height=671\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n赤化後的群眾維權方式<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvODAxN2MxMDZjNjAyNGYzYzNjY2Q0LnBuZz93aWR0aD0xMDgwJmhlaWdodD02MjU\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/8017c106c6024f3c3ccd4.png?width=1080&amp;height=625\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/8017c106c6024f3c3ccd4.png?width=1080&amp;height=625\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/8017c106c6024f3c3ccd4.png?width=1080&amp;height=625\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n總而言之...除了靠西方科技所建立的一切物質事物，其他都在往辛亥前退化，現在的中國，就像是一秦朝沒有被推翻的「秦制朋克」世界。\t\t</div>",
